<h1>Letter Writing Station</h1>
<p>Here is where you can write a letter for UMI. You can write anything your heart desires!</p>
<p>Note: Anything you write will be posted publically on this site, so don't include any sensitive and/or personal information!</p>
<form action="/feedumi" method="post" class="feedumi-form">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="name">Subject:</label>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="description">Message:</label>
    <textarea id="description" name="description" required></textarea>
  </div>
  <button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>




